features: 【 Real Time Location 】 Integrated GPS, WiFi and LBS Positioning. LNCOON gps tracker for kids easily help you location your children in unlimited distance. Visualize current location, movement track and history and SOS alert on LNCOON IOT, available on mobile and PC webpage. Smart updated once A41 start moving, and updated every 10min when stay still. Stand by for 5-7 days.

【 SOS Button 】 LNCOON A41 mini gps tracker specially designed for children, the elderly, pets, autism, amnesia, dementia. Press and hold the SOS button to trigger alert. Or press the SOS button 4 times to actively upload the current location. Suitable for personal safety protection, emergency call for help, children travel monitoring, trajectory monitoring and so on.

【 Geo Fence 】 You can customize your virtual fence within the app. The GPS tracker will trigger instant push alerts to you when your child arrives or leaves school with the A41. The mini GPS tracker is also suitable for locating the location of the elderly and pets. You can set multiple mailboxes to receive alarm notifications.

【 Easy Setup 】 Integrated GPS tracker WiFi and LBS Positioning. LNCOON gps tracker for kids easily help you location your children in unlimited distance. Visualize current location, movement track and history and SOS alert on LNCOON IOT, available on mobile Android and iOS and PC webpage.

【Lightweight and Portable】The device size is 1.77 * 1.57 * 0.59 (in), and only weighs 1.16oz. LNCOON GPS tracking device is compact, lightweight and portable, easy to carry and hide. Equipped with lanyard (8.7in to 19.0in adjustable) and belt clipper, suitable for various wearing scenarios. Type-C charging port can always find a compatible charging cable.

【 Subscription Needed 】 Activating the LNCOON monthly service, you can enjoy the same period of warranty. Cancel anytime, no contracts, no hidden fees. Down to $8.99/month for a 2-year subscription, $10.99/month for 1-year subscription, and you can also start tracking from $16.99/month.
